@node "Document_0" "Installation"
Simply copy the contents of the "GreenDayz" drawer to wherever youy want to have it for permanent storage, as simple as that!
@endnode

@node "Document_1" "Usage"
Using GreenDayz is simple!

I am a big fan of Green Day, and I always found that learning the lyrics is very annoying if you don't have the words in the CD cover, and looking it up on the web, can be a very lengthy and tiresome process, so I decided to gather all the lyrics that I could, and made it into a little E-MailWare program!

Simply run the program, and you get a choice of 5 albums. Simply choose the album you want, and at the side, it has a list of all the available songs for that album. Simply click on one of the song names, and the lyrics will appear in the main listview display on the right. Simple really isn't it?!
@endnode

@node "Document_2" "Author"
This program was written by a 15-year old (soon to be 16) who is mad about Green Day! Which BTW, I'll be going to see a Green Day Concert up in London on the 31st of Jan!!! YESSSSSS!

All the lyrics were taken off the Official Green Day web site, and therefore I take no responsability if I am breaching any copyright laws. http://www.greenday.net/

If you have any more lyrics for any Green Day songs...... why not send them to me? And I can then include them in the next release!

To contact me, you can E-Mail me at: alvaro@enterprise.net

You are reminded that this program is E-MailWare, which means that if you use this program, then you have to send an E-Mail to the author, telling him what you think of it, and any ideas/suggestions you may have on how to improve it (see @{"Future" link "Document_3" 0} section).
@endnode

@node "Document_3" "Future"
For the time being, I'm just going to leave it like a Green Day lyrics viewer. However, sometime in the near future, as soon as I have some free time, I will turn it into a proper lyrics viewer.

This will mean that you will be able to input your own favourite bands, their albums etc, and that people will be able to release "lyric files" for their favourite songs etc.

Watch this space for more info...
@endnode

@node "Document_4" "MUI"

                          This application uses


                        MUI - MagicUserInterface

                (c) Copyright 1992-97 by Stefan Stuntz


MUI is a system to generate and maintain graphical user interfaces. With the aid  of  a  preferences program, the user of an application has the ability to customize the outfit according to his personal taste.

MUI is distributed as shareware. To obtain a complete package containing lots of examples and more information about registration please look for a file called  "muiXXusr.lha"  (XX means the latest version number) on your local bulletin boards or on public domain disks.

